data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 bedroom home with a 2021 roof and greeted by a neatly landscaped front yard. Upon entering, you'll find a spacious front room and the 4th bedroom or office off the foyer. As you continue in, the spacious family room is open and airy, making it easy to host gatherings with guests. The kitchen boasts ample counter and cabinet space, pantry and breakfast bar overlooking the family room. The owner suite is an inviting space with a huge walk-in closet with wardrobe system to maximize space. The master bath features a double sink vanity, garden tub and stall shower. One of the standout features is the screened porch that overlooks a sizable fenced yard! Located a quick few minutes to shopping and entertainment! Assumable FHA loan with 2.375 rate for those who can qualify with Freedom mortgage. See attached docs.
